st. by [@jacob314](https://github.com/jacob314) in [#20517](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20517)\n\n- fix(core): apply retry logic to CodeAssistServer for all users by [@bdmorgan](https://github.com/bdmorgan) in [#20507](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20507)\n\n- Fix extension MCP server env var loading by [@chrstnb](https://github.com/chrstnb) in [#20374](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20374)\n\n- feat(ui): add 'ctrl+o' hint to truncated content message by [@jerop](https://github.com/jerop) in [#20529](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20529)\n\n- Fix flicker showing message to press ctrl-O again to collapse. by [@jacob314](https://github.com/jacob314) in [#20414](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20414)\n\n- fix(cli): hide shortcuts hint while model is thinking or the user has typed a prompt + add debounce to avoid flicker by [@jacob314](https://github.com/jacob314) in [#19389](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/19389)\n\n- feat(plan): update planning workflow to encourage multi-select with descriptions of options by [@Adib234](https://github.com/Adib234) in [#20491](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20491)\n\n- refactor(core,cli): useAlternateBuffer read from config by [@psinha40898](https://github.com/psinha40898) in [#20346](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20346)\n\n- fix(cli): ensure dialogs stay scrolled to bottom in alternate buffer mode by [@jacob314](https://github.com/jacob314) in [#20527](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20527)\n\n- fix(core): revert auto-save of policies to user space by [@Abhijit-2592](https://github.com/Abhijit-2592) in [#20531](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20531)\n\n- Demote unreliable test. by [@gundermanc](https://github.com/gundermanc) in [#20571](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20571)\n\n- fix(core): handle optional response fields from code assist API by [@sehoon38](https://github.com/sehoon38) in [#20345](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20345)\n\n- fix(cli): keep thought summary when loading phrases are off by [@LyalinDotCom](https://github.com/LyalinDotCom) in [#20497](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20497)\n\n- feat(cli): add temporary flag to disable workspace policies by [@Abhijit-2592](https://github.com/Abhijit-2592) in [#20523](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20523)\n\n- Disable expensive and scheduled workflows on personal forks by [@dewitt](https://github.com/dewitt) in [#20449](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20449)\n\n- Moved markdown parsing logic to a separate util file by [@devr0306](https://github.com/devr0306) in [#20526](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20526)\n\n- fix(plan): prevent agent from using ask_user for shell command confirmation by [@Adib234](https://github.com/Adib234) in [#20504](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20504)\n\n- fix(core): disable retries for code assist streaming requests by [@sehoon38](https://github.com/sehoon38) in [#20561](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20561)\n\n- feat(billing): implement G1 AI credits overage flow with billing telemetry by [@gsquared94](https://github.com/gsquared94) in [#18590](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/18590)\n\n- feat: better error messages by [@gsquared94](https://github.com/gsquared94) in [#20577](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20577)\n\n- fix(ui): persist expansion in AskUser dialog when navigating options by [@jerop](https://github.com/jerop) in [#20559](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20559)\n\n- fix(cli): prevent sub-agent tool calls from leaking into UI by [@abhipatel12](https://github.com/abhipatel12) in [#20580](https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/pull/20580)\n\n- fix(cli): Shell autocomplete polish by [@jacob314](https://github.com/jacob314) in [#204